title: Marvel: Crisis Protocol Compatible - Crystal Blue Dice (10) for casual play only
description: This pack contains 10 loose custom made dice for Marvel: Crisis Protocol. These are not official dice, they are fan-made. Because these are hand-made, the size and color may vary slightly from batch to batch.
